ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 202, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 202 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN, with respect to the HEAVY RAINSTORM that affected the province from July 10 to 13, 2016.
